                     Txt2tags Documentation
                     ----------------------
                      http://txt2tags.org


This folder contains the txt2tags main documentation files.
The original files (sources) are in the English folder.
The translations are grouped into language folders.

The documents:

  manpage.man             The manual page (UNIX format)
  markup.html             The Markup Demo (Read this first!)
  rules.html              All the syntax rules (for advanced users)
  sample.html             The txt2tags sample file
  txt2tags-quickref.pdf   The Quick Reference, ready to print
  userguide.pdf           The complete 50 pages User Guide
  writing-book.html       Writing Books with Txt2tags

For a complete list of all txt2tags documentation and its
translations, go to the Documentation page:

  http://txt2tags.org/docs.html

